ted\n368: \n369: ---\n370: \n371: ## Definition of Done\n372: \n373: - [ ] All 107 tasks complete\n374: - [ ] Package installs successfully (`pip install -e .`)\n375: - [ ] Client importable from `agentcube.sdk`\n376: - [ ] All unit tests pass (>80% coverage)\n377: - [ ] All integration tests pass\n378: - [ ] Type checking passes (`mypy`)\n379: - [ ] Linting passes (`ruff`)\n380: - [ ] Documentation complete with docstrings\n381: - [ ] Sync and async APIs working\n382: - [ ] Session management functional\n383: - [ ] Code execution working\n384: - [ ] File operations working\n385: \n386: ---\n387: \n388: ## Dependencies\n389: \n390: | Dependency | Version | Purpose |\n391: |------------|---------|---------|\n392: | `httpx` | >=0.25.0 | HTTP client for API calls |\n393: | `pydantic` | >=2.0.0 | Data validation and models |\n394: | `tenacity` | >=8.0.0 | Retry logic |\n395: | `pytest` | >=7.4.0 | Testing framework |\n396: | `pytest-asyncio` | >=0.21.0 | Async test support |\n397: | `pytest-cov` | >=4.1.0 | Coverage reporting |\n398: | `mypy` | >=1.0.0 | Type checking |\n399: | `ruff` | >=0.1.0 | Linting |\n400: \n401: ---\n402: \n403: ## Verification Commands\n404: \n405: ```bash\n406: # Install verification\n407: pip install -e \"python-sdk/[dev,test]\"\n408: \n409: # Import verification\n410: python -c \"from agentcube.sdk import CodeInterpreterClient, AsyncCodeInterpreterClient\"\n411: \n412: # Unit test verification\n413: pytest python-sdk/tests/test_code_interpreter.py -v\n414: \n415: # Coverage report\n416: pytest --cov=agentcube.sdk --cov-report=term-missing\n417: \n418: # Type checking\n419: mypy python-sdk/agentcube/sdk/\n420: \n421: # Lint verification\n422: ruff check python-sdk/agentcube/sdk/\n423: ```\n424: \n425: ---\n426: \n427: ## API Reference\n428: \n429: ### CodeInterpreterClient\n430: \n431: ```python\n432: from agentcube.sdk import CodeInterpreterClient\n433: \n434: # Initialize\n435: client = CodeInterpreterClient(\n436:     base_url=\"https://api.agentcube.dev\",\n437:     api_key=\"your-api-key\",\n438:     timeout=30.0\n439: )\n440: \n441: # Create session\n442: session = client.create_session()\n443: \n444: # Execute code\n445: result = client.execute_code(\n446:     code=\"print('Hello World')\",\n447:     language=\"python\",\n448:     timeout=10.0\n449: )\n450: \n451: # Upload file\n452: file_ref = client.upload_file(session.session_id, \"/path/to/file.py\")\n453: \n454: # Close session\n455: client.close_session(session.session_id)\n456: ```\n457: \n458: ### AsyncCodeInterpreterClient\n459: \n460: ```python\n461: from agentcube.sdk import AsyncCodeInterpreterClient\n462: \n463: async def main():\n464:     async with AsyncCodeInterpreterClient(\n465:         base_url=\"https://api.agentcube.dev\",\n466:         api_key=\"your-api-key\"\n467:     ) as client:\n468:         session = await client.create_session()\n469:         result = await client.execute_code(\"print('Hello')\", language=\"python\")\n470:         await client.close_session(session.session_id)\n471: ```\n472: \n473: ---\n474: \n475: *AR-027 — Module: sdk-python — Language: Python — Size: M*\n476: *Stage ST-3: Design Complete — Ready for Implementation*\n\n(End of file - total 476 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-027 — SDK CodeInterpreterClient\n\n> **AR ID:** AR-027\n> **Module:** `sdk-python`\n> **Language:** Python\n> **Size:** M\n> **Stage:** ST-3 (Design Complete)\n\n---\n\n## Overview\n\nThe `CodeInterpreterClient` provides a Python SDK for interacting with the Code Interpreter service, enabling secure sandboxed code execution for AI agents and applications.\n\n---\n\n## ST-3.1 — Project Structure and Dependencies\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-027/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775904291195,"end":1775904291214}}}}
